description:
This is our first sponsored meetup. We will have a guest speaker of Optima explaining how real estate can contribute to a good pension. Interesting stuff for any IT independent! ! Please note that the Optima talk will be in Dutch, we can always add talks in the future in French or in English, depending on the demand.

Agenda:

18.30  Welcome

19.00  Presentation Bernard Mortier, Senior Financial Planning Consultant Optima 

20.00  Reception & networking

See you there hopefully!


Pieter & Philip
name: Get to know us + Optima talk (how can real estate contribute to your pension)

description:
Our next meetup will be about Peer to peer economy: a new way of collaboration between IT people, freelancers and customers.The meetup is intented as a brainstom to cover topics such as P2P economy, crowd funding & incubators (to bring ideas to the market).

More detailed agenda will follow and exact location of course. It will probably be in Brussels....
name: Peer to peer economy meetup
